Indonesie l eveil d un archipel

Travel Documentary hosted by Georges Pernoud, published by TV5Monde broadcasted as part of TV5Monde Thalassa series in 2016 - French narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/2/25/Indonesie-l-eveil-d-un-archipel-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Indonesia, the awakening of an archipelago.

Eleven years after the murderous tsunami, the population of the port town of Banda Aceh are learning to live again despite the memory of that terrible day. On the island of Nusa Lembogan, low tide reveals thousands of plots forming a strange chequerboard where the farmers paddle past by canoe...
